The files in this directory pertain to backing up the OpenELIS database.
The script currently installed by default sends the backup files to Seattle. 
a different destination is wanted then there are two generic versions. 

OffSiteBackupLinux.pl is configured for Linux and sends files via ftp.
OffSiteBackupWindows.pl. is configured for Windows and sends files via http.

More information on configuration can be found in BackupHowTo.docx

receive-file.pl is a perl script to be used on the receiving http server.
